**Smörgåsbord ModList Update:** ```2.5.2.12 11:00 EST 27JAN2026

Warning: There's no guarantee you can update the mod list and continue to play in the same save. 
If you are happy with your current playthrough, don't update until you are ready to start a new game. 

Comments:

1. A few hotfixes for EFTX when using vanilla ammo options. Also added a few cool new mods.

2. Fixed the "No NerdPole" issue. It was a setting in "Gears changes SCore" mod. 
You can change settings from that mod in the in-game Mods menu.
Currently, it's set so you can one-block-crouch, and nerdpole-ing is authorized. 

3. Big thanks to both Community Members and Mod Authors who identified issues, reported them, and helped to correct them quickly. 
You guys are great, thank you for everyone's support this week!
You all make maintaining this big list of mods so much easier.
Just so everyone knows, Mod Authors like LittleRedSonja, StallionsDen, ALo, ByteBlazar, Laydor, bdub, sphereii, and many others make maintaining Smorgasbord possible.
I couldn't do it without them!

Mods Removed: 

