Mods Added:

"Loot Abundance Not Ignored" QoL, disabled.
From the Mod Author Frantic Dan: 
There a several loot containers, including zombie loot, that ignore the loot abundance setting, so it is always 100% regardless if you set it to 25% or 200%.
This mod makes it so all containers get the amount of loot that is selected. 
Making the game either easier or harder, depending on your loot setting.

"War3zuk HD Supply Drops" OP, disabled.
This mod add 4 Flares that can be used to call a Supplies Chopper that will drop you the loot box.
HD Building Supply Flare
HD Health Supply Flare
HD Ammo Supply Flare
HD Food Supply Flare
Each drop has it's own custom supplies. 
Flares are found inside Army Trucks & Munitions boxes but are set to Rare finds.
I tested that this works, but not how often the flares show up in loot... 
In testing I saw good weapons dropping too early, that's why it's disabled by default under the OP separator.```
